ActBudget Implementation Act, 2017, No. 1
SubjectOrder Fixing April 1, 2019 as the day on which Certain Provisions of the Act Come into Force
PrecisOrder Fixing April 1, 2019, as the day on which sections 357, 358, 361 and 362, subsections 363(1), (3), (4) and (7) and 364(1) and (4), sections 366 and 367, subsection 368(2) and sections 369, 371, 372, 374, 375, 385, 388 and 389 of the BUDGET IMPLEMENTATION ACT, 2017, No. 1, chapter 20 of the Statutes of Canada, 2017, COME INTO FORCE.
